worker download worker download [&ndash;workflow=] [&ndash;number=] [&ndash;tag=] [&ndash;pattern=]
Synopsis Inside a job, there are two ways to download an artifact:
 with a step using action Download Artifacts with a step script (https://ovh.github.io/cds/workflows/pipelines/actions/builtin/script/), using the worker command: worker download --tag=&lt;tag&gt; &lt;path&gt;
worker download &ndash;pattern=&ldquo;files.*.yml&rdquo;
#theses two commands have the same result: worker download worker download &ndash;workflow={{.cds.workflow}} &ndash;number={{.cds.run.number}}
  worker download [flags]  Options  -h, --help help for download --number string Workflow Number to download from.

